Schedule Reports in Salesforce Classic
Create, change, view, or delete a scheduled report from the Schedule Report page.
Tips for Scheduling Reports (Salesforce Classic)
On the Schedule Report page you can:
Schedule a new or existing report to run in the future and have its results emailed to others.
Change the schedule on a previously scheduled report.
View scheduled jobs for all reports in your organization or view the schedule for just a selected report.
Delete a scheduled run for a selected report.
